sp.p:
Passing neat and exquisite, I protest fair creatures; 
These honours to our solemnity, are liberal and uncommon; 
my spouse and myself with our posterity, shall prostitute
our services, to your bounties, shall we not 
duckling?

The fear put me into a sweat; I cannot help it; 
I am glad I have my throat mine own, and must laugh for
Company, or be laughed at.
